United Medical Corp said itit has requested a meeting of holders of its Swiss Francs 30mln 5-1/8 pct convertible subordinated notes due 1991.    The meeting has been requested in order to amend thenegative pledge and financial covenants which have proved to betoo restrictive in light of the company's activities, it said.    United also said it plans to acquire some of these notes toreduce its exposure to foreign exchange fluctuations. Reuter&#3;